    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Collected specimens (A–C), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (D). Gerromorpha, Gerridae, Microvelia nelsoni. A. Apterous male from Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro (−22.9488, −43.2861). B. Macropterous male from Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro (−22.9335, −43.4450). C. Apterous female from São José do Barreiro, São Paulo (−22.7430, −44.6165). Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
